Cargo.lock
dist
*.node
# napi-rs generates these at build time (napi build --js index.cjs --dts index.d.ts): the CJS addon
# loader + the addon's type surface. Not committed — a fresh checkout has no native engine until built.
index.cjs
index.d.ts
# napi publish scaffolding, generated in CI only (napi create-npm-dir / napi artifacts): the
# per-platform stub packages + the downloaded prebuilts. Never committed — the release job wires
# optionalDependencies from these on the fly, so package-lock.json stays free of unpublished packages.
/npm
/artifacts
/prebuilds
